## 7-15. Additional Patterns (Summary)

### 7. SIM Swap Fraud
**Method:** Attacker convinces carrier to port number to their SIM  
**Impact:** Enables 2FA bypass for banking fraud  
**Detection:** Verify request via call to registered number

### 8. Premium SMS Fraud  
**Method:** Malware subscribes user to premium services  
**Impact:** $10-30/month unexpected charges  
**Detection:** Monitor `sms_to_premium_numbers` field

### 9. Roaming Fraud
**Method:** Permanently roaming SIM avoids taxes  
**Impact:** Regulatory violations  
**Detection:** `days_in_roaming > 90`

### 10. eSIM Swap (NEW 2024)
**Method:** Remote provisioning attack  
**Impact:** Account takeover without physical SIM  
**Detection:** Require video call for eSIM activation

### 11. AI Deepfake Social Engineering
**Method:** Voice cloning to impersonate customer  
**Impact:** Bypass voice authentication  
**Detection:** Liveness detection, video verification

